{"tid":1496430,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"神社求「光復香港」遭改「一個中國」 平野鈴子：不要破壞日本","createTime":"2019-08-22T13:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T14:04:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd8b339d8bae53106161c9ab5af91742a6d234d","tid":1496430,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpSexcik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpSexcik.jpg&h=7eff1a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國在國內外藉由煽動「愛國心」，藉此壓制香港反送中運動，就連位於日本神社也難逃波及。被譽為「日本反送中第一人」、和服模特兒平野鈴子在臉書上發文表示，一塊位於京都八坂神社的許願牌本來寫著「光復香港時代革命」，沒想到卻遭人劃掉並寫上「一個中國不動搖」的字樣。平野鈴子對此表示，「不要破壞我的日本」。<br />\n<br />\n平野鈴子在臉書上表示，「又發生了一次，這次是京都八坂神社。到底是什麼樣的瘋子才會擾亂他人的祈願？」平野玲子表示，過往明治神宮、靖國神社也遭到這類的破壞。平野玲子表示，「神社是祈願的地方，不是一個希望別人不幸的地方。不要破壞我的日本。」<br />\n<br />\n除了「光復香港 時代革命」的許願牌（繪馬）遭塗改成「一個中國不動搖」以外，一旁則掛了寫有「國家安康 祖國昌盛 和平統一 一國兩制」字樣的許願牌。<br />\n<br />\n另外，近日港人發動「#eye4HK」挑戰，各地網友也紛紛上傳以手遮右眼的自拍照。長期關注香港反送中運動的平野玲子，也在Instagram 上傳以手遮眼的自拍照。平野鈴子表示，為了香港的自由、為了東亞的未來、為了我愛的國家、為了下一代，我將繼續奮鬥。無論犧牲什麼，都要奮鬥到最後。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZbE2fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZbE2fd.jpg&h=3e43cf05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2892839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2892839&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=0fa8623b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2892839&h=e36e2aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2892839</a>"},{"pid":"3bfab47e0911097db07170d69fd1992361f1fb30","tid":1496430,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBjf8.jpg&h=8a441805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgzvoHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgzvoHP.png&h=79a62f84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca88826b48af503b6d5c4a1a485847c1a8365c7f","tid":1496430,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"多謝日本"}]}